title: Mixtape Game: Did You Get Gonorrhea?
description:
Mixtape Game Hosted by Falen // 

Sadly, you’re at a funeral. Everything is going as planned, but when aunt Anita goes to
Hit play on amazing Grace, the world’s worst song that could play at a funeral plays instead. What song plays? //

﻿You’ve been with your hs sweetheart your whole life. You just turned 45, and you’re getting divorced. You’ve never been alone. You’ve never been in the dating scene. What song plays as you begin this new chapter? // 

You’re drunk in Vegas. You find your dream partner (or so you think in your drunken state). You get married that same night. What is your wedding song?
